n of errors suggests a systemic storage or connection failure on the part of `cartservice`.\n\n### Stance:\nThe hypothesis that `cartservice`'s inability to access its cart storage is the root cause is **SUPPORTED**.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"FailedPrecondition\", \"Can't access cart storage\", \"rpc error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"The 'FailedPrecondition' error indicating 'Can't access cart storage' suggests a persistent inability of cartservice to communicate with its storage.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error status code 'FailedPrecondition' with detail 'Can't access cart storage.' raised.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据调用链数据分析，从2025年06月18日01:10:10Z到2025年06月18日01:27:10Z期间存在一系列异常调用链及状态码。\n\n### 延迟分析\n1. **CheckoutService**\n   - `frontend-1` 调用 `checkoutservice-0`, 延迟显著增加，正常是 143518ms，异常是 599026ms，延迟倍数约 4.17\n\n2. **EmailService**\n   - `checkoutservice-0` 调用 `emailservice-2`, 延迟显著增加，正常是 682ms，异常是 1993ms，延迟倍数约 2.92\n\n3. **ShippingService**\n   - `checkoutservice-0` 调用 `shippingservice-1`, 延迟显著增加，正常是 205ms，异常是 1668ms，延迟倍数约 8.13\n\n### 错误分析\n- 前端服务报告多个 HTTP 500 错误：\n  - `aiops-k8s-01` 上的 `frontend-1` 服务有 69 次错误\n  - `aiops-k8s-04` 上的 `frontend-0` 服务有 55 次错误\n\n### 关键发现与拓扑图分析\n- 主要异常集中于 `CheckoutService` 和 `EmailService`、`ShippingService` 的调用链。\n- 根据拓扑结构，`CheckoutService` 调用 `EmailService` 和 `ShippingService`，并且两者都表现出显著延迟，表明这两个服务可能是异常的根因。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时长 682ms，异常时长 1993ms，延迟倍数 2.92\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时长 205ms，异常时长 1668ms，延迟倍数 8.13\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_